Ngokusho kukaKaizer Kganyago okhulumela iSABC ukuqinisekisile ukumiswa kukaMaboi emsebenzini. "Singakuqinisekisa ukuthi ngeke azwakale emoyeni uMaboi okwamanje, kodwa ngeke sikwazi ukusho okwamanje isizathu salesi sinqumo,"kusho uKganyago. OLUNYE UDABA:U-Andile Jali ‘uhambise ingoduso’ yakhe emndenini Ngesikhathi ebuzwa abeSunday World ukuba aphawule ngokuxoshwa kwakhe uMaboi, uvele wadinwa wavala ucingo. Imibiko evelile ithi le ntokazi ixoshiwe ngemiva kokuthi imihlangano abenayo ne-SABC angabi nemiphumela emihle. Kuleyo mihlangano, uMaboi wacelwa ukuthi axolise kuKganyago kodwa kwanhlanga zimuka nomoya ngoba washaya phansi ngonyawo - News24
